realityETH.name: Reality Module
abi: constructor(address _owner, address _avatar, address _target, address _oracle, uint32 timeout, uint32 cooldown, uint32 expiration, uint256 bond, uint256 templateId)
event AvatarSet(address indexed previousAvatar, address indexed newAvatar)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event ProposalQuestionCreated(bytes32 indexed questionId, string indexed proposalId)
event RealityModuleSetup(address indexed initiator, address indexed owner, address indexed avatar, address target)
event TargetSet(address indexed previousTarget, address indexed newTarget)
function addProposalWithNonce(string proposalId, bytes32[] txHashes, uint256 nonce)
function buildQuestion(string proposalId, bytes32[] txHashes) pure returns (string)
function executeProposal(string proposalId, bytes32[] txHashes, address to, uint256 value, bytes data, uint8 operation)
function executeProposalWithIndex(string proposalId, bytes32[] txHashes, address to, uint256 value, bytes data, uint8 operation, uint256 txIndex)
function generateTransactionHashData(address to, uint256 value, bytes data, uint8 operation, uint256 nonce) view returns (bytes)
function getQuestionId(string question, uint256 nonce) view returns (bytes32)
function getTransactionHash(address to, uint256 value, bytes data, uint8 operation, uint256 nonce) view returns (bytes32)
